{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rendagor</strong> is a run-and-gun game set in a near future where human labor has been almost completely replaced by humanoid drones controlled by corporate artificial intelligence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The player will control one of Rendagor Corporation's drones through some 2D levels with top-down pixel art graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> This demo includes the first three levels of the Rendagor story mode in which you will be guided by the main AI of Rendagor Corp. <i>(RCAI)</i>\u00a0and the first level of Arcade Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story Mode:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight against animals altered by the pollution produced by Rendagor Corp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372070/extras/ANIMALI_ALTERATI.gif?t=1737555702\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the first two weapons available to the drones: Energy Laser and a small machine gun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372070/extras/WEAPON.gif?t=1737555702\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Improve your drone using the R-Chips you find around the map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372070/extras/UPGRADE_FIG.gif?t=1737555702\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spend the R-Coins you find in the chests to purchase ammunition or repair/recharge kits in the InstaShops scattered around the maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372070/extras/SHOP.gif?t=1737555702\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve small puzzles and explore the maps well for additional loot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372070/extras/ENIGMI.gif?t=1737555702\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kill bosses at the end of each level to advance to the next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372070/extras/BOSS.gif?t=1737555702\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Arcade Mode:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face waves of random enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372070/extras/SPAWN_WAVE.gif?t=1737555702\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the end of each wave you will receive an R-Chip and can choose one among three random bonuses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372070/extras/END_WAVE.gif?t=1737555702\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kill the final boss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372070/extras/LAST_WAVE_BOSS.gif?t=1737555702\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Note: Demo content may differ in some aspects from the full game.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3372070?t=1737555702","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3372070?t=1737555702","capsule_image